RESULT: At control module 3, the input side shows ~12 V between the 12V (+) cable and the 0V (−) cable, while the output side shows ~0 V between its 12V (+) and 0V (−) cables. The continuity test between Control Input Cable (+) 3 and Control Output Cable (+) 3 indicates an open circuit (very high resistance).
